{
  "stem": "22237.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had terrible stories in there-- that Jewish doctors trying to inject Gentiles with poisonous medication.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had bankers that would swindle Jews out of their money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I was walking to school, and people were actually reading this and-- young people, old people, of all ages.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by the time I got to school, I couldn't learn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- I-- I wasn't thinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't listening to the teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was thinking about that [NON-ENGLISH], what they had read in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because-- not that I stopped to read it, but somehow, once in a while, we had gotten a hold of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my brothers would bring it home, and we would read it just out of interest, what they had to write.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going to school was getting harder and harder.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and this-- and that was about '33.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they had-- in 1934, I remember-- I'm talking about the highlights that come to my mind-- then they had the infamous Hitlerjugend, Hitler Youth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a group that Hitler had somehow came up with, this Hitlerjugend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were given-- this was depression time, there wasn't much to-- to wear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this Hitlerjugend, these young boys, were given beautiful uniforms, so that they would feel good, similar to what-- how a Boy Scout feels when he gets a new uniform.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were young people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they could actually do whatever they wanted with the children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They usually-- you know, they usually-- they didn't stop adult people, but children had a hard time, because you usually-- When you saw them come-- I remember when I walked to school, and I saw them come around the corner, I would turn around, or go on the other side, or try to avoid them.",
      "word_count": 55
    }
  ],
